## 10. Hal Positif yang Perlu Dipertahankan

1. ✅ **Prepared Statements konsisten** — Anti SQL injection
2. ✅ **CSRF Protection** — Setiap form
3. ✅ **Role-Based Access Control** — 4-level role system
4. ✅ **Activity Logging** — Audit trail
5. ✅ **Flash Message System** — UX feedback baik
6. ✅ **Responsive Design** — Mobile menu & layout
7. ✅ **Accessibility** — `prefers-reduced-motion` support
8. ✅ **Print Styles** — CSS print media queries
9. ✅ **Schema terstruktur** — 20+ tabel dengan FK & constraints
10. ✅ **Seed Data** — Admin user & 31 kecamatan siap pakai
